Package: GEEMiHC
Type: Package
Title: Detecting sparse microbial association signals
       from longitudinal microbiome data based on generalized estimating equations
Version: 1.0
Author: Han Sun
Maintainer: Han Sun <sunh529@mails.ccnu.edu.cn>
Description: GEEMiHC detects sparse microbial association signals 
         between microbiome and a host phenotype from longitudinal 
         microbiome data. As a special case of longitudinal data, 
         cross-sectional microbiome data can be also applied.
Imports: phyloseq, cluster, compositions, permute, PGEE, vegan, ape, aSPU, MiSPU, devtools
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/SunHan5/GEEMiHC
